            <description><![CDATA[<p ALIGN="center"><a href="http://blog.photo.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#url=http://static16.photo.sina.com.cn/orignal/4933cc36t7d2b0f0e032f" TARGET="_blank"><img SRC="http://static16.photo.sina.com.cn/middle/4933cc36t7d2b0f0e032f&amp;690" /></A></P>
<p ALIGN="center"><br />
